### Get List of Images 

curl --location 'http://localhost:4566/restapis/7wq0gujrcp/local/_user_request_/list?created_at=2025-10-05&file_name=test.png' \
--header 'Content-Type: application/json' \
--data ''

### Upload Images

curl --location 'http://localhost:4566/restapis/7wq0gujrcp/local/_user_request_/upload' \
--header 'Content-Type: application/json' \
--data '{
    "file_name" : "test.png",
    "file_content" : "data:image/jpeg;base64,",
    "metadata" : {
        "type" : "jpeg"
    }
}'

### Get Images details 

curl --location 'http://localhost:4566/restapis/leywikvcdu/local/_user_request_/get?id=96b37d68-ff2e-4cc9-9cbf-ae8c1baa898e' \
--data ''

### Delete image

curl --location --request DELETE 'http://localhost:4566/restapis/leywikvcdu/local/_user_request_/delete' \
--header 'Content-Type: application/json' \
--data '{
    "id" : "3bb92917-ee8e-4749-bc20-487bc15aab51"
}'
